# Keeps wwwroot/ present so the API boots even before the Vite SPA is built into wwwroot/app.
# The static-web-assets manifest lists wwwroot/ as a content root; PhysicalFileProvider throws
# DirectoryNotFoundException at startup (Development env) if it is absent. The built SPA (wwwroot/app/)
# is produced by `pnpm build` locally or by the Dockerfile for images, and stays gitignored.
